data.description: Welcome to the epitome of luxury living in the exclusive Creekside at Flintrock Falls neighborhood. This magnificent 4-bed, 4-bath home is a true sanctuary, offering an unparalleled blend of sophistication, comfort, and tranquility. With a private backyard oasis boasting a sparkling pool and a sprawling one-acre lot, this property provides the perfect escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life, while its convenient location puts you close to shopping, fine dining and entertainment. As you step inside the home, you are immediately captivated by modern elegance. The open concept design creates a seamless flow, allowing for effortless entertaining and an abundance of natural light. The spacious chef's kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, featuring ample counter space, top-of-the-line appliances, and freshly painted custom cabinetry. The master retreat is a true haven of relaxation, with direct porch access that invites you to enjoy your morning coffee while overlooking the serene surroundings. The master bathroom is a masterpiece in itself, boasting a luxurious garden tub, a separate walk-in shower, and dual vanities. No detail has been overlooked in this home, with fresh, modern paint throughout that enhances the contemporary ambiance. Elegant details and fixtures can be found in every corner, showcasing the impeccable craftsmanship and attention to detail. Step outside into your own private paradise - the expansive backyard beckons you to unwind and enjoy the Texas sunshine. Take a dip in the inviting pool, perfect for those hot summer days, or simply relax on the patio and savor the tranquility of your surroundings. With an acre of land to call your own, there is plenty of space for outdoor activities and creating lasting memories with family and friends. Don't miss your opportunity to own this extraordinary residence in the highly sought after Lake Travis ISD and experience a lifestyle that is nothing short of exceptional.
